l = TemplateLookup(cache_impl='mock')
l.put_string('x',
    """
            <%page cached="True" />
            ${y}
        """)
t = l.get_template('x')
self._install_mock_cache(t)
assert result_lines(t.render(y=5)) == ['5']
assert result_lines(t.render(y=7)) == ['5']
assert isinstance(t.cache.impl, MockCacheImpl)
